org.harctoolbox.ircore

Class Pronto

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.harctoolbox.ircore.Pronto
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ShortPronto

    public abstract class Pronto
extends Object
    This class, containing only static functions, allows for the creation of integer arrays and strings containing Pronto (CCF) form of the signal. It cannot be instantiated, since there are no "Pronto"s, it is just IrSignals in "another coordinates".
